JOHANNESBURG - FNB customers have been left stranded and frustrated as the bank's online systems were down for hours. The bank was hit by a major outage affecting its internet banking, mobile app and card transactions. Numerous users took to social media to report issues in processing transactions online and at physical pay points. FNB said it has resolved the issues with the digital channels and bank cards fully functional. Dear FNB Eswatini customer, please be notified of the below.  #FNBEswatini #FNB pic.twitter.com/3EvFDwtL4R  FNB... today of all days @FNBSA pic.twitter.com/tmIDYx9AIw  FNB uvaliwe, labaNtu be Durban July bayikhiphe yonke imali. pic.twitter.com/PHFhvp38cu 